snippet: Juan Martin del Potro is unlikely to be fit enough to play in next month's Australian Open, the Argentine told a news conference on Tuesday....
lead_paragraph: Juan Martin del Potro is unlikely to be fit enough to play in next month's Australian Open, the Argentine told a news conference on Tuesday.

headline.main: Del Potro Unlikely to Be Fit for Australian Open
